      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pot with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped onion </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1670347691384-x200.jpg",
