            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail and slice your <strong>leek[s]</strong> into chunky rounds and wash to remove any grit</p><p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> on the diagonal into discs</p><p>Chop your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into small bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1670347696023-x200.jpg",
