      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine <strong>half </strong>the<strong> grated garlic</strong> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>creamy single soy </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) – this is your <strong>garlic cream</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1670347706157-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
