            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabattas</strong> in half</p><p>Spread the <strong>garlic cream </strong>over the <strong>ciabatta halves </strong>and drizzle with a little<strong> vegetable oil </strong>– these are your<strong> garlic ciabattas</strong></p><p>Once ready, transfer the charred corn to a bowl, reserve the baking tray</p><p>Add the <strong>garlic ciabattas </strong>to the reserved tray and put the tray under the grill for 3-4 min or until golden and toasted – these are your <strong>garlic toasts</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1670347721156-x200.jpg",
