          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1670347721156-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chowder</strong> in bowls and taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> if needed</p><p>Top with the <strong>charred corn</strong>, <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and<strong> chopped chives </strong>– this is your<strong> charred corn & creamy leek chowder</strong></p><p>Slice the<strong> garlic toasts</strong> into triangles and sprinkle over the <strong>smoked sea salt</strong> – these are your <strong>smoked salt toasts</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>smoked salt toasts</strong> to the side and enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
